{{index/hero-header
  didSubmit=(readonly application.didSubmit)
  onSubmit=(action (mut application.didSubmit) true)
  onFormVisibilityChange=(action (mut isHeroFormShowing))}}

{{index/nav-bar
  isButtonVisible=(not isHeroFormShowing)
  didSubmit=(readonly application.didSubmit)
  onSubmit=(action (mut application.didSubmit) true)}}

{{#index/section-objection childrenClass='col-md-6 offset-md-1' as |objection|}}
  {{#objection.question}} Not yet comfortable scrambling an egg? {{/objection.question}}
  {{#objection.answer}} No matter your experience -- kitchen zero or culinary hero -- our tested recipes and 6-week lesson plan will help cooks of all levels build (or brush up on!) the knowledge, skills, and confidence you'll need for a delicious meal. {{/objection.answer}}
{{/index/section-objection}}

{{#index/section-info as |info|}}
  <a class='anchor' id='menu' />
  {{#info.title}} Menu {{/info.title}}
  {{#info.lead}} Impress Mom with this deceptively simple 3-course, gourmet meal: {{/info.lead}}

  {{#meal-menu class='row' as |menu|}}
    <div class='col-md-7 p-relative d-flex flex-column'>
      {{#each menu.dishes as |dish|}}
        {{#info.lead tagName='h4' class='text-center d-md-none'}} {{capitalize dish.slug}} {{/info.lead}}
        <div class='card {{dish.slug}} {{if dish.active 'sim-hover'}}'
          onmouseover={{action menu.activate dish}}
          onmouseout={{action menu.deactivate dish}}>
          <img class='card-img-top' src='{{dish.imageUrl}}'>
          <div class='card-body d-md-none'>
            <p class='card-text text-center'> {{dish.description}} </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>

    {{#info.content tagName='ul' class='col-md-5 d-none d-md-flex flex-column justify-content-between'}}
      {{#each menu.dishes as |dish|}}
        <li class='i-{{dish.slug}} {{if dish.active 'sim-hover'}}'
          onmouseover={{action menu.activate dish}}
          onmouseout={{action menu.deactivate dish}}>
          {{dish.description}}
        </li>
      {{/each}}
    {{/info.content}}
  {{/meal-menu}}
{{/index/section-info}}

{{#index/section-objection childrenClass='col-md-6 offset-md-4' as |objection|}}
  {{#objection.question}} Is Mom vegan? Need a gluten-free option? {{/objection.question}}
  {{#objection.answer}} Each lesson focuses on building your knowledge and skills, and includes suggested modifications for popular diets. Your Mother's Day recipes will come with inline notes for vegetarian & vegan options. {{/objection.answer}}
{{/index/section-objection}}

{{#index/section-info as |info|}}
  <a class='anchor' id='six-free-lessons' />
  {{#info.title}} Six Free Lessons {{/info.title}}

  {{#course-calendar class='row' as |calendar|}}
    <div class='col-md-6'>
      {{#info.lead}} In the weeks leading up to Mother's Day, you will learn: {{/info.lead}}
      {{#info.content tagName='ul'}}
        {{#each calendar.lessons as |lesson|}}
          <li class='i-{{lesson.slug}} {{if lesson.active 'sim-hover'}}'
            onmouseover={{action calendar.activate lesson}}
            onmouseout={{action calendar.deactivate lesson}}>
            {{lesson.description}}
          </li>
        {{/each}}
      {{/info.content}}
    </div>

    <div class='col-md-6 col-lg-5 offset-lg-1 d-flex flex-column mt-3 mt-md-0'>
      {{#power-calendar
        center=calendar.center
        onCenterChange=(action (mut calendar.center) value='date')as |power|}}
        {{power.nav}}
        {{#power.days
          startOfWeek=1
          minDate=calendar.min
          maxDate=calendar.max
          dayIsDisabled=calendar.dayIsDisabled as |day|}}
          {{course-calendar/day calendar day}}
        {{/power.days}}
      {{/power-calendar}}
    </div>
  {{/course-calendar}}
{{/index/section-info}}

{{#index/section-objection childrenClass='col-md-6 offset-md-3' as |objection|}}
  {{#objection.question}} Worried about the time commitment? {{/objection.question}}
  {{#objection.answer}} You will only need 2 - 4 hours per week to keep up with our weekly lessons; your full Mother's Day meal will need about 6 hours you can split between two days. Plus, our digital course is designed for your modern schedule, where a weekly 6pm class might not be a flexible enough solution. {{/objection.answer}}
{{/index/section-objection}}

